  "page": "Harvest Hall",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Stormlands.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The stormlands and the semi-canon location of Harvest Hall\"><img alt=\"The stormlands and the semi-canon location of Harvest Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/The_Stormlands.png/400px-The_Stormlands.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/The_Stormlands.png/600px-The_Stormlands.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/The_Stormlands.png/800px-The_Stormlands.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 61.1%; left: 19.4%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -6px; top: -6px; width: 12px; font-size: 12px;\"><img alt=\"The stormlands and the semi-canon location of Harvest Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Harvest Hall\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/18px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/24px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 90%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; top:-0.15em; left: -3em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Harvest Hall</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a> and the semi-canon location of Harvest Hall\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Harvest Hall</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Selmy\" title=\"House Selmy\">House Selmy</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Dornish Marches</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> According to a semi-canon source, it is located near the eastern border of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, northeast of <a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a>, northwest of <a href=\"/index.php/Blackhaven\" title=\"Blackhaven\">Blackhaven</a> and south of the <a href=\"/index.php/Cockleswhent\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cockleswhent\">Cockleswhent</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harvest_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When he was a youth at Harvest Hall, <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> played a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spin_the_bottle\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Spin the bottle\">kissing game</a> with his cousins.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harvest_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harvest_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> considered returning to Harvest Hall after being removed from the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>, but he did not want to endanger his cousins. Barristan instead left <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> to find <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harvest_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 63\">Chapter 63</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_55\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 55\">Chapter 55</a>, The Queensguard.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rt